%h3 Popular posts
- @popular_posts.each do |post|
  %p
    .link-to-post
      %h5
        %span.votes= post.net_votes
        <i class='icon-arrow-up'></i>
        = link_to post.title, post_path( post )
      %h5
        %span.author
          =(link_to post.author, { :action => :author, :id => post.author })+", "
        %span.date= post.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y")
